---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 mt-16">
  <div class="container-page py-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-4">
    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold text-sm">B</span>
        <span class="font-display font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">Beyond<span class="text-blue-600">10</span></span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 max-w-md">
        Beyond MPC and BiPC. Beyond10 helps Class IX–X students in India discover the full menu of careers, entrance exams, top-paying paths, and scholarships — sourced and free.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Discover</h3>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/careers" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900">Careers</a></li>
        <li><a href="/exams" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900">Competitive exams</a></li>
        <li><a href="/top-paying" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900">Top-paying careers</a></li>
        <li><a href="/streams" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900">After 10th — streams</a></li>
        <li><a href="/scholarships" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900">Scholarships</a></li>
        <li><a href="/colleges" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900">Top colleges</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Project</h3>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/about" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900">About + sources</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about#methodology" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900">Methodology</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about#trust" class="text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900">Trust &amp; safety</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-stone-200">
    <div class="container-page py-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
      <p>© {year} Beyond10. Built for India's students.</p>
      <p>Data current as of April 2026 — see <a href="/about#sources" class="underline hover:text-slate-700">sources</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
